" Normal mode mappings
nnoremap k j
nnoremap j h
nnoremap l l
nnoremap i k
nnoremap h i
nnoremap <S-i> 5k
nnoremap <S-k> 5j
nnoremap <S-j> 5h
nnoremap <S-l> 5l

" Visual mode mappings
vnoremap k j
vnoremap j h
vnoremap l l
vnoremap i k
vnoremap <S-i> 5k
vnoremap <S-k> 5j
vnoremap <S-j> 5h
vnoremap <S-l> 5l

" Operator pending mode mappings
onoremap k j
onoremap j h
onoremap l l
onoremap i k
onoremap <S-i> 5k
onoremap <S-k> 5j
onoremap <S-j> 5h
onoremap <S-l> 5l

